original_title: ကျွန်မက နှင်းဆီပါ မောင်
overview: When a rich man is rich and endowed with money every night, when a servant who has been a servant in the house of his master has become rich for the sake of luck, I have to look at the rivalries of my master and lover.
tagline: When a rich man is rich and endowed with money every night, when a servant who has been a servant in the house of his master has become rich for the sake of luck, I have to look at the rivalries of my master and lover.
title: I'm Rose, Darling
